title: Ep. 1132 - The Signature Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha gets a call from Natu kaka who informs him that he has forgotten to sign a cheque. But Jetha informs him that he cant go to the shop now as he has a meeting with a client. How will Jetha handle this situation?

title: Ep. 1133 - Daya Apolozies To Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha forgets his file at home because of Daya. He goes back home to get the file and returns to the shop.

title: Ep. 1134 - Iyer Gets Jealous - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita waits for Jetha's call. Meanwhile, Iyer calls Babita and she picks up thinking that it was Jetha. Iyer gets jealous and questions her. He then tells her not to wait for his call and that he'll handle the situation.

title: Ep. 1135 -Babita Looks For Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita waits for Jetha so that she can get the file. But when Babita calls Jetha he tells Nattu Kaka to attend the call.

title: Ep. 1136 - Jetha Gets A Card For Babita - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Natu Kaka and Baga suggest Jetha get a 'Sorry' card for Babita. Jetha finally finds the note where he had noted down the number. Jetha thanks Daya for her prayers for which he managed to find that note.

title: Ep. 1137 - Jetha's Sweet Gesture - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha forgets to bring what Champaklal told him to. Jetha hands him over the apology card that he had got for Babita.

title: Ep. 1138 - Tapu Fools Jetha And Daya - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu pretends to be Champaklal and Jetha starts explaining himself. Later, Daya and Jetha look for the differences and found out that it was Tapu who tried fooling them. Tapu asks Daya for a favor.

title: Ep. 1139 - Tapu Tries To Convince Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu and Daya convince Jetha to get Tapu a seasoned bat. Jetha refuses to spend a huge amount for a bat

title: Ep. 1140 - Jetha Goes Mad Out Of Excitement- Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sonu calls Tapu Sena to help her out but they are locked inside. Jethalal overhears Natu and Baga's conversation and thinks they have received a big order.

title: Ep. 1141 - Bhide Creates Chaos - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide calls everyone and explains to them the mistakes Tapu Sena has committed. Champaklal comes and asks Tapu about what exactly happened.

title: Ep. 1142 - Champaklal's Good Old Days - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha finally gets bat for Tapu and some mangoes for everyone. A guest arrives who happens to be Champaklal's friend.

title: Ep. 1143 - Champaklal Has Decided - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal decides to go to village. Jetha calls Baga to know if he had got the tickets. Champaklal is shocked to know the highly-priced tickets. He is adamant to go by railways.

title: Ep. 1144 - Jetha Finds A Way - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A customer comes to Jethalal's shop who happens to be an agent. Jetha asks him if he can help get him two tickets.

title: Ep. 1145 - The Great Grand Confusion - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha gets tickets by train and Champaklal's friend gets tickets by bus.

title: Ep. 1146 - Daya Gets Romantic - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya calls up Jetha to inform him that she won't be cooking anything for dinner.
